narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: A great course that explores the complicated terrain that is adoption. Great, interesting reading, and for the papers you can really write about what fascinates you.
It interesting and provides a variety of approaches and angles to understanding adoption. It is however, sometimes too much reading.
Absolutely take it. Wonderful professor, wonderful subject matter.
Highly recommend. Great professor, interesting books!
